Olkilikuai oyaka Petero esirit te Yerusalem


1  Neaku etoning'o apa ilkipaareta o lalashera ootii Yudea nchere etang'amutua sii ninche loreren ororei le Enkai. 
2  Ore pee eilepu Petero alotu Yerusalem, neishankarrarre lelo le muratare ninye, 
3  aajoki, “Ishomo iyie ajing enetii Lmemurata, nilo ang'arie endaa.” 
4  Kake eiterua Petero aibalakinye ina bae osupatei, ajoki, 
5  “Enkanasa naji Yopa apa atii naomonito: naainepu enduaata, e ntoki natiu anaa olkarasha oing'uaa shumata oitadouni too lcholo pokira oong'uan, nelotu enatii. 
6  Neaku ore pee akurraki nkonyek aing'or, nadol ajo, ng'uesi e nkop oo nkejek maa ong'uan, o ng'uesi e ong'ata, o ntokitin naaikurtutari o motonyi e shumata. 
7  Naning sii oltoilo laajoki, ‘Inyo, Petero, teyiang'a naa nosa.’ 
8  Kake atejo, ‘Olaitoriani, Mme neijia, amu eitu ae kata eim enkutuk ai entoki e nturuj anaa enemesinya.’ 
9  Kake aatawalikia ilo toilo ajoki te nkata e are eing'uaa keper, ‘Ore entoki naitisinya Enkai, nimintaa iyie enturuj.’ 
10  Neikoni neijia katitin uni, neitokini aainyaaya pooki keper. 
11  Naa ng'ura, eitashe ina kata ltung'ana okuni ti auluo ina aji nikitii, eirriwuaki eing'uaa Kaisaria pee epuonu enatii. 
12  Naajoki Enkiyang'et maturubare, nemapik olng'ash. Naairiamariyie kulo alashera pokira ile; nikijing enkaji e ilo tung'ani. 
13  Neliki ninye iyiook olmalaika otoduaa te nkaji enye, nejoki, ‘Irriwai ltung'ana Yopa, mpoto Simon oji Petero; 
14  pee kilotu aliki irorei lijeunye, iyie o enkaji ino pooki.’ 
15  Neaku ore pee aiter airo nedoiki ninche Enkiyang'et Sinyati, anaa apa enatadoikio iyiook te nkiterunoto. 
16   Nadamu ororei lo Laitoriani, otejo apa, te nkare eibatisishe Yohana, kake keibatisae intae te Nkiyang'et Sinyati. 
17  Amaa naa te neishoo Enkai ninche enkishorunoto neeijo enapa naishoo ninye iyiook pee kiruk Olaitoriani Yesu Kristo kara nanu ng'ae oibooyo Enkai?” 
18  Ore pee ening ninche nena baa negira neisis Enkai nejo, “Eishoo naa Enkai sii ninche Loreren enkirridunoto nayau puaan.”

Esirit e Antiokia


19   Neaku ore lelo ooisardakieki to lapa sina otupukuo te nkaraki Stefano nepuo o metabaiki Foenike o Kupro o Antiokia, naa Lyahudi ake einosakita ilo rorei. 
20  Kake etii kulikae lenye, ltung'ana ooing'uaa Kupro o Kirene, laa ore pee ebaya Antiokia neinosaki sii ninche Ilyunani, nelikioo Olaitoriani Yesu. 
21  Neiriamariyie engolon o Laitoriani ninche; ore lkumok ooiruko neibelekenyakino Olaitoriani. 
22  Nebaiki ina nataasa ninche nkiyiaa e ina sirit natii Yerusalem: neirriwaa ninche Barnaba meshomo Antiokia. 
23  Ore pee ebaya, nedol enkiaas e mpiris e Nkai, neng'ida, neisisaki pooki nejoki metaa ilooisiligayu to Laitoriani te nkitashoto nauno oo ltauja. 
24  Amu oltung'ani supat ninye obore Enkiyang'et Sinyati o enkirukoto. Neponikino Olaitoriani olturrur sapuk. 
25  Neaku eshomo Barnaba Tarso aing'oru Saulo. 
26  Ore pee etum, neriku Antiokia. Neya olari olulung'a etumore ake ina sirit, neiteng'en esiamo kitok e ilo orere; naa te Antiokia eiteraki aajo ilooiteng'eni Ilkristiano.


27  Ore te nena olong'i nepuonu loibonok le Nkai ooing'uaa Yerusalem aapuo Antiokia. 
28   Ore obo lenye oji Agabus neinyototo aibonu te Nkiyang'et ajo kelotu olameyu kitok e nkop pooki; (neewuo ina aaku too nkolong'i e Klaudius). 
29  Nedung ilooiteng'eni anaa ake enaidima oltung'ani, aajo keirriwaki eretoto ilalashera oomanya Yudea. 
30  Neiko neijia, neyaki lpayiani too nkaik e Barnaba o Saulo.

